    {
      "chinese": "賽夏族原本居住在平原，海外人士到來失去土地，只好遷往山裡，沿著山稜線及河流往上，遷移到現在的五峰、南庄和獅潭居住。",
      "ab": "SaySiyat ’ima rowaSek ray pa:aw, wa:i’in noka Say kabih no wasal, ’oemaeh Simari’, SaySiyat rae:iw ila naehan ray koko:ol. kakoko:ol a kaba:la’ manakiS ila ray ’isahini kilapa:, pinSa’o:olan(lamsong), Sawi’ rowaSek.",
